Description: Lingmo Desktop SDK - development files
 Lingmo SDK is the developer toolkit for building Lingmo Desktop
 applications. It provides CMake packages, C++ libraries, and QML
 modules for theme management, UI controls, animation, and system
 integration.
 .
 This package contains the development files.
